{"tid":2093604,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"一個有效濕疹治癒方法分享","createTime":"2020-07-04T03:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T16:17:04.000Z","uid":137088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9678e1da2308d73f8c97bea2e37aa6f0e11f88e","tid":2093604,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"近排肺炎多左度體温，發現經常係35.8-36.2度左右，屬於偏低，正常體溫係36.5-37.0，因此本人屬寒性體質。跟左下面方法濕疹好左8-9成。<br />\n<br />\n治癒方法：<br />\n多進食温熱食物<br />\n多做運動，曬太陽<br />\n沖暖水涼<br />\n飲黑糖薑母茶（温熱去寒）<br />\n<br />\n温熱食物表及詳請：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.relativehumanity.com.tw/cm/cm297.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.relativehumanity.com.tw%2Fcm%2Fcm297.htm&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=8814c047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.relativehumanity.com.tw/cm/cm297.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cb5b5c7547e4e2c66e9d0ef5cfde1f27681eb0dc","tid":2093604,"uid":292896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T16:17:04.000Z","msg":"如果熱底呢"}]}